snippet.title: Historical & Situational Assessment - Daniel Schmachtenberger, Wade Davis @ Virtual Burning Man 2020
snippet.description:
This was part of a longer stream recorded and published by PlayAlchemist Community, and it was uploaded for educational purposes only. The full stream is available here: https://youtu.be/qc_y9jNUky4

The playlist titled "Essentials at The Seeking" on this channel offers a collection of clips discussing what may be deemed some of the most fundamental concepts to our endeavor. 

Essentials at The Seeking playlist link: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLeRBa-Ner4BsP0ypB-FnB70-KiKZFtRpG

This youtube channel and its operators are not affiliated with the hosting organization or the speakers in this interview.
